new feature of the Chrome Dev

00:01:46.020 --> 00:01:49.280
Tools that lets you preview the
value of JavaScript variables

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.770
in line as you debug.

00:01:50.770 --> 00:01:52.605
The feature works
with minified scripts,

00:01:52.605 --> 00:01:56.250
